b. excessive salt intake
c. diet low in fruit, vegetables, dairy (low in $\mathrm{K}^{+}$and $\mathrm{Ca}^{2+}$ )
d. defects in $\mathrm{Na}^{+}-\mathrm{K}^{+}$pumps
